<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p><strong>西昌篇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200814/22c17e06063241c3b208b429423e194f.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200814/ef4115571e4b4f72b3502d9e68af9a82.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200814/9c20fe1aed5040ba9027970fa9d339e5.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一座春天栖息的城市</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">西昌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被誉为太阳城、月亮城、航天城</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是一座春天栖息的城市</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这里冬暖夏凉、四季如春</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">美景、小吃，数不胜数</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">千万别错过~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200814/9f052b448c5547b7824dfd8de8901876.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>胡仲平丨摄 </p>
<p>01</p>
<p><strong>西昌美景打卡</strong></p>
<p><strong>邛海湿地公园</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200814/d02558835e5c48368a921583cdd7710f.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>胡仲平丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">邛海湿地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总面积达到2万亩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">连片接壤的生态湿地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将邛海紧紧呵护</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">形成独特的湿地景观</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200814/c2bb1e13b21f4c7ba47399c33d3d36f7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>李小平丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">湿地划分为西波鹤影</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梦里水乡等区域</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200814/c587dd46779a4d60b5034499441a0fce.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>曲木子撒丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然每个区域主题不一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但都美得沁人心脾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并且花香四溢、飞鸟成群</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200814/8f42b7240a4b4d30be60164590e5cd3a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200814/01c01e9901ed4d218cab9aecf72a8131.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200814/4162b4769fb040bfb8b75b341a495a5e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200814/7ba7c5f642034773a83ad02920b85df5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>李星丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">邛海是西昌的必游打卡地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">月亮女儿雕塑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成为许多游客喜爱的打卡点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200814/52cccf3ec2c3417f99acc18cc1432be0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>李小平丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">悠闲地在邛海逛一逛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">站在湖边看日出、日落</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">感受朦胧诗意般的西昌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也是不虚此行</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200814/c912c819e0b84b94b5c1ee4d77df5bd4.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200814/5aa02d20a9fd4a0986ba5254f479c773.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200814/57f263895def4945b8b7505ca0e98a0b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200814/58424d3591e1475daf6aeecc09c61aa9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>胡小平 何淑芬 李星 邹森丨摄 </p>
<p>02</p>
<p><strong>西昌美景打卡</strong></p>
<p><strong>海河天街</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200814/b519843dab1d47d993522740da8abd8d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>邹森丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">海河</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从东南到西北，穿城而过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">河水清澈明亮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200814/41f39694560e486e806012c282986038.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>张家让丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这里有</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">沿河傍水而建的街道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">游人如织，热闹非凡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它就是海河天街</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200814/d61090b2b666484383ff7008dc6970fc.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200814/433400945be14714a88f920be835f16e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200814/d7bff70c1fdb482db4d4690cb9be79cf.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>邹森 李星丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">火把节来这里逛一逛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等暮色降临，华灯初上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">坐在河边酒吧的摇椅上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">点一杯Mojito</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">微醺着感受</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">海河天街的温柔和热闹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200814/f111edec546c43acbc1daec80bc3eed8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>李星丨摄 </p>
<p>03</p>
<p><strong>西昌美景打卡</strong></p>
<p><strong>建昌古城</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200814/6fa8424608d04c238b03c390c627d067.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">建昌古城</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有着悠久的历史</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是西昌的文化符号</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200814/6da4f1b75bf4409e8ebd4f634960a6e7.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>李星丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在这里能看见许多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古遗址、古石刻、古建筑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它们星罗棋布</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是西昌城区</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">目前保存最完整的古城遗迹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200814/6419a37f928f4c1fa93151ed80b624bd.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200814/f4831abbb9db4fd688acb3a4fc6e08a3.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200814/47e9a1da1f81420a9b51be3d61e87d84.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200814/aee75109921f404399d68bdd87423aaa.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200814/f3e50a056cfd470e91b3ea742b8329a0.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>李星丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">火把节来这里逛一逛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">去大通门点杯茶</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">背靠城墙品茶</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">感受西昌人民的市井烟火气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">多快哉 ~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200814/571bfa90983749e0b10e53e0797f6af1.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>李星丨摄 </p>
<p>04</p>
<p><strong>精彩活动打卡</strong></p>
<p><strong>阿惹妞</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200814/84b27bad050846a1bd298d6b70f48395.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>成大器丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">到了西昌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要是想感受</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">异彩纷呈的民俗文化</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那你一定要</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">去看一场《阿惹妞》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200814/41a2f511cad749c9ac1ef135dede4720.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>成大器丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《阿惹妞》是中国</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 首台彝文化风情实景火秀 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 已被列入</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 四川省级非物质文化遗产名录 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200814/bc721210df93456981d7f6e8899741b5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>李星丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“火”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">作为彝族的生命图腾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">贯穿全剧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从民族源起的脚步</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">到彝族世俗风情的展开</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从阿惹妞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">情与爱的相遇相知</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">到火把节的热烈欢腾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">呈现了“火”作为一个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">民族情感的载体</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而展开的生命传奇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">表演时间：8月14、15日晚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">表演地点：火把广场民俗村寨内</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200814/ca7265e21f7846c1ac7ccd93db33ea2a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>李星丨摄 </p>
<p>05</p>
<p><strong>精彩活动打卡</strong></p>
<p><strong>“云端”开海节</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“开海节”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">民间俗称赶海、祭海</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是千年渔文化</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">的一种古老习俗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200814/ce0f94b60dd642df961edbde9eb54e3a.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>钟玉成丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">受疫情影响</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于8月14日</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在月色风情小镇举办的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 西昌2020年 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> “最美西昌渔游邛海”开海节 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">整个活动将通过网络直播</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以“云”开海形式进行</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">主打“云上开幕、线上参与”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200814/ff2c47aca1af4f87a614e7df2291e7a2.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200814/61e620bfbd394c33bde73a271cf82194.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200814/f98f0b309b7a42259f1270c90e6ba360.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">18年开海节渔王前三名</p>
<p>李星丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个火把节</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让我们远程体验</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">捕鱼、吃鱼的乐趣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">隔屏感受</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风调雨顺鱼满仓的开海盛况</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200814/f6c3bee0ac06411496cb9ba690044e92.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>李星丨摄 </p>
<p>06</p>
<p><strong>西昌美食</strong></p>
<p><strong>各色特色小吃</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">西昌美食数不胜数</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">美味的邛海鱼首当其冲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">家喻户晓的一鱼三吃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在海边大小餐馆都能预定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200814/4cd2e7e1184146288b56b7a1051cb7ef.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>网络丨来源 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一鱼三吃即</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鱼头做的南瓜鱼头汤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鱼排做的油炸酥鱼排</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鱼肉做的青椒麻辣鱼或酸菜鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">口味丰富、回味无穷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200814/19ce37194fd6433481d2016633316f02.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>网络丨来源 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">另一道美食是醉虾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用刚从邛海捞出的小青虾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">佐以白酒、小米辣、花椒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">姜蒜、米醋、酱油等调料</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将玻璃碗盖子盖上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闷5至7分钟左右</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这道菜就成了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">入口有酒醇香</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肉感细腻、鲜嫩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还能感觉到虾在舌尖跳舞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200814/9d255a4feab649958352aee42e45a20f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>李星丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了这些“海味”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在西昌市区的小巷子里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">藏着美味小吃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拌洋芋、拌凉粉、冰粉、串串等</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">实惠又美味，值得打卡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">入股不亏~~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200814/d2eaedb5683d414ca5f4afe352cc267e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200814/66c62fbcb4b4465194fbb8eed2f66f72.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200814/8fba169c639141b884391579c065d4f9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200814/fde2072cbb5b4c9aa178224ac418d4ae.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200814/51b020c041924cee829d7173dd875305.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>李星丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不管是酸辣可口的拌洋芋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还是凉爽安逸的红糖冰粉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">或是奇妙口感的炸卷粉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在这里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总有一款是你的爱</p>
<p>07</p>
<p><strong>特色伴手礼</strong></p>
<p><strong>彝族漆器、南红玛瑙、文创产品</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200814/308073a3edb44a788566800b8ed1893d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>李星丨摄 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">彝族漆器</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">采用酸枝木、樟木作坯胎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">野生土漆和各矿物颜料作髹饰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">纯天然，无毒，经久耐用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200814/6bf547446f7b4dea8720245491c9b787.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>李星丨摄 </p>
